/// \mainpage The Error Code Xero Robot Framework
///
/// This software framework is the robot framework used by Error Code Xero.  It is
/// divided into two seperate libraries.
///
/// The library org.xero1425.misc contains various source code that is independent of
/// the WPILib library.  This source code could be used in any contenxt.
///
/// The library org.xero1425.base contains the base architecture for the WPILib based
/// robot source code.  Error Code Xero does not use the Command framework from WPILib
/// but rather has its own framework.  This framework along with many other useful classes
/// for creating a robot, tuning a robot, and diagnosing problems on a robot are found in
/// this library.
///

